## Why LightAPI?

LightAPI is a modern, async-ready Python REST API framework designed for rapid development and production use. It combines the best features of FastAPI, Flask, and Django REST Framework while maintaining simplicity and performance.

### üéØ Key Benefits
- **‚ö° Instant CRUD APIs**: Generate full REST APIs from SQLAlchemy models in seconds
- **üöÄ High Performance**: Built on Starlette/Uvicorn with async support
- **üìñ Auto Documentation**: OpenAPI/Swagger docs generated automatically
- **üîê Security First**: Built-in JWT authentication and CORS support
- **üíæ Smart Caching**: Redis integration with intelligent cache management
- **üîç Advanced Queries**: Filtering, pagination, sorting, and search out of the box
- **‚úÖ Data Validation**: Comprehensive request/response validation
- **üìÑ Configuration Driven**: YAML-based API generation
- **üîß Extensible**: Custom middleware and endpoint customization

---

## Who is LightAPI for?

- **üè¢ Backend developers** who want to ship APIs fast, with minimal code
- **üìä Data engineers** needing to expose existing databases as RESTful services
- **üöÄ Prototypers** and **startups** who want to iterate quickly and scale later
- **üèóÔ∏è Enterprise teams** building microservices and internal APIs
- **üéì Educators** teaching REST API development and best practices
- **üîÑ Migration projects** moving from other frameworks to modern async Python

---

## ‚ú® Features Overview

### üîß Core Features
- **Automatic CRUD Endpoints**: Generate REST APIs from SQLAlchemy models
- **Async/Await Support**: High-performance async request handling
- **OpenAPI Documentation**: Auto-generated Swagger UI and ReDoc
- **JWT Authentication**: Secure token-based authentication
- **CORS Support**: Cross-origin resource sharing configuration
- **Redis Caching**: Intelligent caching with TTL and invalidation
- **Request Validation**: Comprehensive input validation and error handling
- **Database Agnostic**: Works with PostgreSQL, MySQL, SQLite, and more

### üöÄ Advanced Features
- **Advanced Filtering**: Complex queries with multiple criteria
- **Pagination & Sorting**: Efficient data retrieval with customizable pagination
- **Search Functionality**: Full-text search across multiple fields
- **YAML Configuration**: Define APIs without writing Python code
- **Custom Middleware**: Extensible middleware system
- **Error Handling**: Comprehensive error responses and logging
- **Performance Monitoring**: Built-in performance metrics and caching stats
- **Hot Reloading**: Development server with auto-reload

